FILTER (?x != ns:m.01bk3n)
FILTER (!isLiteral(?x) OR lang(?x) = '' OR langMatches(lang(?x), 'en'))
ns:m.01bk3n ns:time.recurring_event.date_of_first_occurance ?x .
}
